title: Why Leaked Pentagon Documents Are Still Circulating on Twitter and Discord
description: Twitter and the social media platform Discord have policies about how they would handle the material. But those rules have gray areas and can be unevenly enforced.

title: See How Real AI-Generated Images Have Become
description: Human eyes — and even technology — often struggle to identify images created by artificial intelligence. Experts fear that may hasten an erosion of trust in media, in government and in society.
